phoria Patches 1.2 for Reimagined </a>\n</ul>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><b><big><strong>Some of the <font color=\"2ed159\">texture pack</font> used in this modpack... </strong></big></b></summary>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/fresh-animations\">FreshAnimation </a>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/fresh-animations-extensions/files?page=1&pageSize=20\">FreshAnimation+Details </a>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/fresh-animations-extensions/files?page=1&pageSize=20\">FreshAnimation+All_extensions </a>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/fresh-animations-extensions/files?page=1&pageSize=20\">FreshAnimation+Quivers </a>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/fresh-animations-extensions/files?page=1&pageSize=20\">FreshAnimation+Emissive </a>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/primes-hd-textures\"> Prime's HD Textures </a>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/enhanced-boss-bars\"> Enhanced Boss Bars</a>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/foliage+\"> Foliage+</a> (if you are laggy, disable it)\n<li>And 6 more...\n\n</ul>\n</details>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/r4KPSO3o/images/f9a681a76a5ca5f6e44d59e9a25e896e2afd39de.png\" alt=\"\">\n</p>\n<center>\n<strong>How it looks ingame</strong>\n</center>\n<center>\n<hr>\n</center>\n\n<p><Big><strong><b>🌐Join the community</big></strong></b><br/>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/nE3Dey4G9s\"><img alt=\"Discord\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1140735965367910532?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=%23ffffff&label=Discord&color=%23567bc7&link=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FnE3Dey4G9s\"></a>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\n<img alt=\"Modrinth Downloads\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/r4KPSO3o?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&color=%23246626\">\n</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp